    "accordions_7hFxxC": {
      "type": "accordions",
      "blocks": {
        "topic_34mEtj": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "MADE FROM 100% FRUITING BODIED MUSHROOM",
            "text": "<p>It's not as saucy as it sounds (unfortunately).<br/><br/>The fruiting body is the part of the mushroom is where all the good stuff lives (bioactive ingredients - polysaccharides and triterpenes) from. </p><p>Rule 101 of buying any mushroom supplement: if it isn't made from the fruiting body, then don't bother. </p><p>Some not so good mushroom supplement brands use the 'mycelium' part instead of the fruiting body. This is a root-like structure grown on grains like rice or oats. When this is farmed, you get a mix of mycelium and grain—more filler, less fungi. Better off feeding it to the birds.<em> </em></p><p>Stick with the filthy fruiting body for the real deal.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "topic_izcVfG": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "MADE BY DUAL EXTRACTION METHOD",
            "text": "<p>It may sound like the 20th sequel of The Bourne Identity film franchise. But, it's not. Much more boring but arguably much more important (sorry Matt).<br/><br/>It's basically how we get all those juicy bioactive ingredients out of the mushroom fruiting body. Dual extraction uses both water and alcohol to pull out the full spectrum of bioactive goodies. </p><p>The water extracts the immune-boosting polysaccharides, while the alcohol traps the triterpenes, which are great for their anti-inflammatory and antioxidant benefits. </p><p>No alcohol or water remains in the final dried product. This method ensures you're getting the purest filth possible.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "topic_YVNCDq": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "OUR PRODUCTS ARE 3RD PARTY TESTED",
            "text": "<p>To ensure double safety and the best purity, each batch is third-party tested for nasties and heavy metals by a third party.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "topic_3Rgixh": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "OUR MUSHROOMS ARE ORGANIC",
            "text": "<p>Not sure this one needs a drop down as it's pretty self explanatory, but yeah, our mushrooms are Organic. Lovely stuff. </p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "topic_34mEtj",
        "topic_izcVfG",
        "topic_YVNCDq",
        "topic_3Rgixh"
      ],
